  <strong>2025-02-19</strong> – <a href="https://github.com/insin/control-panel-for-twitter">control-panel-for-twitter</a> <a href="https://github.com/insin/control-panel-for-twitter/releases/tag/v4.9.0">v4.9.0</a>
  <div><em>Browser extension which gives you more control over your Twitter timeline and adds missing features and UI improvements - for desktop and mobile</em></div>
  <details><summary>v4.9.0 release notes</summary><p>Visit the <a href="https://soitis.dev/control-panel-for-twitter" rel="nofollow">Control Panel for Twitter website</a> for installation links, more information about the extension, and FAQs. Follow <a href="https://twitter.com/ControlPanelFT" rel="nofollow">@ControlPanelFT</a> on Twitter or <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/soitis.dev" rel="nofollow">@soitis.dev</a> on Bluesky for updates.</p>
<h2>Changes</h2>
<ul>
<li>Added an option to prevent the next video autoplaying on mobile (enabled by default) - videos will loop instead</li>
<li>Changed the "Hide total tweet metrics" option to "Hide profile header metrics", as metrics in the profile header now change when you switch profile tabs</li>
<li>Fixed hiding Views and the Share Tweet button in the mobile media viewer</li>
<li>Fixed Follow/Following button styles in the mobile media viewer when you're using the option to uninvert them elsewhere on Twitter</li>
<li>Fixed processing Premium checks in mobile media viewer video info</li>
<li>Fixed hiding the "You aren't verified yet" Premium upsell on your own profile page</li>
</ul>
